{"tid":1098961,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得身為外貌協會嘅自己，好難識人","createTime":"2019-04-09T12:37:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T13:54:29.000Z","uid":237096,"like":12,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3c895ab2adf925320c8cbe43dea83363273526aa","tid":1098961,"uid":237096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T12:37:43.000Z","msg":"太高質同靚仔，又怕高攀唔起，唔敢識<br />\n太低質同樣衰，就連交流講多句嘢都唔想<br />\n想識個極普普通通樣嘅，但每次人地又睇我唔上眼<br />\n反而有試過高質靚仔flirt我，我會好唔自然地迴避同自卑得制婉拒咗，一來自己唔係新鮮籮白皮，二來覺得靚仔多人溝，好無安全感<br />\n亦試過樣衰兼無身型但有錢嘅溝我，我都接受唔到，覺得樣重要過錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e44528d93a658bb3b7b69d0f19f4c9972751421","tid":1098961,"uid":208722,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T12:38:11.000Z","msg":"留名睇負評數目"},{"pid":"486762284696d7dfc04e50e6acc354deacef631b","tid":1098961,"uid":131696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T12:39:38.000Z","msg":"你想知樓主係咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127490814174cada1da318ac9689ed575088a008","tid":1098961,"uid":131696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T12:39:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知樓主係咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7a4abb81e293ecf52899208bcba06e0c2209cfd3","tid":1098961,"uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T12:50:23.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1841afb862739506134327fab5599b10504f1b6f","tid":1098961,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T12:55:43.000Z","msg":"聽講基佬好貪玩<br />\n樓主小心係啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e324e72aaaba815d3c14d9dce98d7428d3f6520f","tid":1098961,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T12:55:48.000Z","msg":"你性格太on9<br />\n冇人會鍾意你"},{"pid":"8e44009683aaf5a1460d31